 premium/discount between PENDLE perpetual price and spot index. The platform's off-chain order book aggregates pricing data while settlement occurs on-chain via their custom rollup. Funding payments are automatically debited/credited to trader positions at each hour mark. Aevo's combined options and perpetuals ecosystem can create unique funding rate pressure during high volatility periods."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
